name: Mackenzie US High Yield Bond Index ETF (CAD-Hedged)
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive USD High Yield Corporates Total Market Hedged to CAD Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in high yield corporate bonds issued in US dollars, either directly or indirectly, with its foreign currency exposure hedged back to the Canadian dollar.
